        "description": "绑定了Qos策略的独享物理专线不允许创建共享物理专线，请联系商务经理。"
      },
      {
        "errorCode": "IllegalParam.ResourceGroupId",
        "errorMessage": "Invalid ResourceGroupld value.",
        "description": "指定的资源组非法或不存在"
      },
      {
        "errorCode": "Forbidden.VpconnCrossBid",
